{"tid":498329,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"牛熊一係唔玩，一玩就要得近","createTime":"2017-12-13T16:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T11:40:28.000Z","uid":81236,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1f05b0b8c284446fd52fce6e4e3bdd5dcf67ca9e","tid":498329,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"牛熊既用途就係槓桿，愈近既槓桿愈強<br />\n<br />\n如果玩超遠牛熊既我買正股唔好？<br />\n<br />\n所以玩牛熊就一定要夠近！<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如你睇完上面好認同既話就請你必須要小心牛熊操作<br />\n<br />\n買賣時請留意以下幾點：<br />\n1.）必須要有心理準備total loss或者賺好多，但無論你贏或輸都唔好太在意，輸左可以上黎講兩句發洩下，但切忌贏左就意氣風發，因為下個就到你。<br />\n<br />\n2.）係超貼價牛熊中，止賺比止蝕更重要，唔識走既話你帳面賺幾多都無用。你估你你係股神次次可以係最高/最低位買？<br />\n<br />\n3.）每日到價就收手，切忌再入/反手。<br />\n<br />\n4.）千奇唔好掂70%以上街貨牛/熊，因為最好味。<br />\n<br />\n我見好多人最近因爲大上大落好多人輸/贏錢上黎出post，但無論你係邊一面既人都好，牛熊係非單邊市既事候只宜小注，否則最後贏既永遠只有莊家。<br />\n<br />\n玩牛熊比正股需要既心理質素強好多，比起一切技術分析重要。"},{"pid":"426becb103a4907bf1e1e87a4a5bbbd00385be75","tid":498329,"uid":85405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又學到野"},{"pid":"2d1ff7ca954819a10bf92a5cb08d09d93f627aef","tid":498329,"uid":131259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa86641efa74b89d5371cbfbef409625d8b5579","tid":498329,"uid":9527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"巴打覺得牛熊窩輪兩者之間要揀的話 有咩因素要睇"},{"pid":"0d6cc88e66ffdc8b8e9fdc22a1f53fdf176bb926","tid":498329,"uid":67270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打覺得牛熊窩輪兩者之間要揀的話 有咩因素要睇</blockquote><br />\n同問，牛熊同輪最大分別同賣點係咩"},{"pid":"f0416b45d6444d6d89e6e75b31ce38a248a29a64","tid":498329,"uid":126042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打覺得牛熊窩輪兩者之間要揀的話 有咩因素要睇</blockquote><br />\n同問，牛熊同輪最大分別同賣點係咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n牛熊有少少似槓桿炒股票，可以當佢期貨咁trade 相對來講時間損耗同引伸波幅影響比輪細，主要跟正股股價/期指行可能正股升一檔佢就行一格咁<br />\n<br />\n而輪基本係期權既變種版， 可以睇下bs option pricing model 了解下會影響權價既因素，操作上如果正股係爆緊上去既好似700 由380到430果段既 你炒輪應該會賺得多d 因為你會贏埋個引伸<br />\n<br />\n留名等樓主補充"},{"pid":"fa08d4b6c6d6c311434ce24fc93e495f1df0a3ad","tid":498329,"uid":27970,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:44:32.000Z","msg":"玩牛熊死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35176af7e58192eaecc80d1227363b78031844e5","tid":498329,"uid":126042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩牛熊死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講野咁毒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b00697361673477419079427d5e3f64d0b8ad2","tid":498329,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T23:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩牛熊死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講野咁毒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b32d2db28945a737aa291e5203f60584eaf78eb","tid":498329,"uid":124436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T23:26:12.000Z","msg":"牛熊證發行商 / 輪商<br />\n<br />\n邊間比較好？ 有邊間一定唔可以買"},{"pid":"c59966edba026dc21a12ff65d029e3ac567a127e","tid":498329,"uid":106782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:06:47.000Z","msg":"如果股災爆個下，買熊咪好易贏?"},{"pid":"0c3afbb29235ac6bbafbebc62b13214f1ee74c3e","tid":498329,"uid":94551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T00:07:06.000Z